Q.  Was it just a case of rustiness?
PADRAIG HARRINGTON:  Suppose so. Put it down to that.
Q.  How was the concentration?
PADRAIG HARRINGTON:  Same. Bit rusty. Could have been better. Definitely. It was going well for a good while and just hit a few poor, slack shots. Concentration really. On the par five I laid up into the water and on the last hit a poor wedge with the wind swirling. I didnÃ¢ï¿½ï¿½t really settle on the shot. Lost three shots on those two holes.
